---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Waboom" description="Learn about Waboom's mission to transform businesses through AI-powered automation">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About Waboom"
				tagline="Transforming businesses through intelligent automation and AI-driven solutions."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/about.webp"
					alt="Waboom team working on AI solutions"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Our Mission</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						At Waboom, we're on a mission to revolutionize how businesses operate through intelligent automation. We specialize in building end-to-end AI-powered solutions that streamline processes, reduce errors, and free up valuable human resources for strategic tasks.
					</p>
					<p>
						Our journey began with a simple realization: many businesses are held back by manual, time-consuming processes that could be automated through AI. We've proven this with our successful implementation of purchase order and invoice automation systems that have transformed operations for our clients.
					</p>
					<p>
						Today, we're expanding our vision to help more businesses embrace the power of AI automation, offering both consulting services and custom-built solutions that deliver measurable results.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Our Expertise</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<ul>
						<li>AI-Powered Process Automation</li>
						<li>Custom AI Module Development</li>
						<li>ERP System Integration</li>
						<li>Workflow Optimization</li>
						<li>Strategic AI Consulting</li>
						<li>Implementation & Support</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Waboom</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						<strong>Proven Track Record:</strong> We've successfully implemented AI solutions that have reduced manual processing times consistently and essentially eliminated errors.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>End-to-End Partnership:</strong> From initial consultation to implementation and ongoing support, we're with you every step of the way.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>Custom Solutions:</strong> We build modular, scalable solutions that adapt to your specific business needs and integrate seamlessly with your existing systems.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	.content ul {
		list-style-type: none;
		padding: 0;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.content ul li {
		background: var(--gradient-subtle);
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
